---
title: Indian Spiced Beef with Roasted Squash and Chutney Drizzle
description: This fragrant Indian spiced beef gets its flavour from a delicious Indian Spice. A mild and tasty base of spices is balanced with fresh cucumber raita and sweet chutney, all on a bed of pillowy rice. Divine!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/indian-spiced-beef-952c8f07.jpg
